{
    
    "ingredients": [
        {
            "name":"1 lb butter - softened" 
        },
        {
            "name": "1 1/2 C Brown Sugar"
        },
        {
            "name": "1 C white sugar"
        },
        {
            "name": "3 eggs"
        },
        {
            "name": "2 tsp vanilla"
        },
        {
            "name": "1 1/2 tsp Baking soda"
        },
        {
            "name": "1/2 tsp salt"
        },
        {
            "name": "5 C flour (we like 3 C white and 2 C whole wheat)"
        },
        {
            "name": "2 C semi-sweet chocolate chips"
        },
        {
            "name": "1-2 C shredded coconut"
        }
        
    ]
    Cream the butter and sugar together, then beat in the eggs and vanilla
    Mix in salt, soda and flour
    Add chocolate chips and coconut
    Bake 8-10 minutes at 350 F
}